{
  "name": "zhihu-fisher",
  "displayName": "Zhihu Fisher",
  "description": "VSCode 刷知乎摸鱼插件 | 支持浏览知乎推荐、热榜、搜索内容，提供沉浸模式、图片大小调整、灰色模式、智能伪装模式。支持评论区、收藏夹等功能。",
  "version": "0.4.5",
  "author": "CrispyChicken",
  "engines": {
    "vscode": "^1.82.0"
  },
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://github.com/crispyChicken999/zhihu-fisher-vscode"
  },
  "icon": "./icon.png",
  "publisher": "CrispyChicken",
  "keywords": [
    "zhihu",
    "fisher",
    "知乎",
    "摸鱼",
    "推荐",
    "热榜",
    "搜索",
    "收藏夹",
    "评论区",
    "沉浸模式",
    "智能伪装"
  ],
  "categories": [
    "Other"
  ],
  "activationEvents": [],
  "main": "./dist/extension.js",
  "contributes": {
    "commands": [
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.refreshHotList",
        "title": "刷新热榜",
        "icon": "$(refresh)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.refreshRecommendList",
        "title": "刷新推荐",
        "icon": "$(refresh)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.dislikeRecommendItem",
        "title": "不喜欢该内容(减少推荐)",
        "icon": "$(thumbsdown)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.favoriteRecommendItem",
        "title": "收藏到收藏夹",
        "icon": "$(star)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.favoriteSearchItem",
        "title": "收藏到收藏夹",
        "icon": "$(star)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.dislikeAuthor",
        "title": "不再推荐该作者(屏蔽作者)",
        "icon": "$(account)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.searchContent",
        "title": "搜索知乎内容",
        "icon": "$(search)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.refreshCollections",
        "title": "刷新收藏夹",
        "icon": "$(refresh)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.loadMoreCollectionItems",
        "title": "加载更多收藏项",
        "icon": "$(arrow-down)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.openCollectionItem",
        "title": "打开收藏项"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.refreshCollection",
        "title": "刷新收藏夹",
        "icon": "$(refresh)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.openCollectionInBrowser",
        "title": "在浏览器中打开收藏夹",
        "icon": "$(link-external)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.openCollectionItemInBrowser",
        "title": "在浏览器中打开",
        "icon": "$(link-external)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.showCollectionItemImage",
        "title": "查看图片",
        "icon": "$(zoom-in)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.openArticle",
        "title": "打开文章"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.openInBrowser",
        "title": "在浏览器中打开",
        "icon": "$(link-external)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.showFullImage",
        "title": "放大缩略图",
        "icon": "$(zoom-in)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.setCookie",
        "title": "设置Cookie",
        "icon": "$(key)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.clearCollectionCache",
        "title": "清理收藏夹缓存",
        "icon": "$(clear-all)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.setMediaModeNormal",
        "title": "正常显示",
        "icon": "$(eye)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.setMediaModeMini",
        "title": "迷你模式",
        "icon": "$(screen-normal)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.setMediaModeNone",
        "title": "全部隐藏",
        "icon": "$(eye-closed)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.setMiniMediaScale",
        "title": "设置迷你模式缩放比例",
        "icon": "$(zoom-in)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.setAnswersPerBatch",
        "title": "设置回答预加载数量",
        "icon": "$(list-ordered)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.configureBrowser",
        "title": "配置浏览器",
        "icon": "$(browser)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.setCustomChromePath",
        "title": "自定义浏览器路径",
        "icon": "$(folder-opened)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.openFeedback",
        "title": "问题反馈与建议",
        "icon": "$(feedback)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.starOnGitHub",
        "title": "觉得不错？GitHub上点颗星吧~",
        "icon": "$(star-full)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.buyMeCoffee",
        "title": "请我喝杯咖啡吧~",
        "icon": "$(heart)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.showAbout",
        "title": "关于",
        "icon": "$(info)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.showGuide",
        "title": "使用说明",
        "icon": "$(book)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.restartExtension",
        "title": "重启扩展",
        "icon": "$(refresh)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.showTroubleshootingGuide",
        "title": "故障排除指引",
        "icon": "$(tools)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.toggleDebugMode",
        "title": "调试模式",
        "icon": "$(bug)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.openZhihuUrl",
        "title": "浏览指定链接",
        "icon": "$(link)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.refreshMyCollections",
        "title": "刷新我创建的收藏夹",
        "icon": "$(refresh)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.refreshFollowingCollections",
        "title": "刷新我关注的收藏夹",
        "icon": "$(refresh)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.loadMoreMyCollections",
        "title": "加载更多我创建的收藏夹",
        "icon": "$(arrow-down)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.loadMoreFollowingCollections",
        "title": "加载更多我关注的收藏夹",
        "icon": "$(arrow-down)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.openMyCollectionsInBrowser",
        "title": "在浏览器中打开我创建的收藏夹",
        "icon": "$(link-external)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.openFollowingCollectionsInBrowser",
        "title": "在浏览器中打开我关注的收藏夹",
        "icon": "$(link-external)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.removeFromCollection",
        "title": "取消收藏",
        "icon": "$(notebook-delete-cell)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.createCollection",
        "title": "创建收藏夹",
        "icon": "$(add)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.deleteCollection",
        "title": "删除收藏夹",
        "icon": "$(trash)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.toggleDisguise",
        "title": "切换智能伪装",
        "icon": "$(eye)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.showDisguiseCache",
        "title": "查看伪装缓存状态",
        "icon": "$(info)"
      },
      {
        "command": "zhihu-fisher.showChangeLog",
        "title": "更新日志",
        "icon": "$(history)"
      }
    ],
    "viewsContainers": {
      "activitybar": [
        {
          "id": "zhihuFisher",
          "title": "知乎摸鱼",
          "icon": "$(book)"
        }
      ]
    },
    "views": {
      "zhihuFisher": [
        {
          "id": "zhihuRecommendList",
          "name": "推荐",
          "icon": "$(star)",
          "contextualTitle": "知乎推荐"
        },
        {
          "id": "zhihuHotList",
          "name": "热榜",
          "icon": "$(flame)",
          "contextualTitle": "知乎热榜"
        },
        {
          "id": "zhihuSearchList",
          "name": "搜索",
          "icon": "$(search)",
          "contextualTitle": "知乎搜索"
        },
        {
          "id": "zhihuCollectionsList",
          "name": "收藏",
          "icon": "$(bookmark)",
          "contextualTitle": "知乎收藏"
        }
      ]
    },
    "viewsWelcome": [
      {
        "view": "zhihuRecommendList",
        "contents": "加载知乎推荐中...\n[刷新](command:zhihu-fisher.refreshHotList)\n[设置Cookie](command:zhihu-fisher.setCookie)\n\n如果遇到浏览器问题，可以尝试：\n[安装浏览器](command:zhihu-fisher.configureBrowser)\n[自定义浏览器路径](command:zhihu-fisher.setCustomChromePath)"
      },
      {
        "view": "zhihuHotList",
        "contents": "加载知乎热榜中..."
      },
      {
        "view": "zhihuSearchList",
        "contents": "点击搜索按钮查找知乎内容..."
      },
      {
        "view": "zhihuCollectionsList",
        "contents": "加载知乎收藏中..."
      }
    ],
    "submenus": [
      {
        "id": "zhihu-fisher.mediaDisplayMenu",
        "label": "多媒体显示模式"
      }
    ],
    "menus": {
      "view/title": [
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.refreshHotList",
          "when": "view == zhihuHotList",
          "group": "navigation@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.refreshRecommendList",
          "when": "view == zhihuRecommendList",
          "group": "navigation@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.searchContent",
          "when": "view == zhihuSearchList",
          "group": "navigation@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.refreshCollections",
          "when": "view == zhihuCollectionsList",
          "group": "navigation@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.openZhihuUrl",
          "when": "view == zhihuHotList || view == zhihuRecommendList || view == zhihuSearchList || view == zhihuCollectionsList",
          "group": "abrowser@5"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.toggleDisguise",
          "when": "view == zhihuHotList || view == zhihuRecommendList || view == zhihuSearchList || view == zhihuCollectionsList",
          "group": "bmode@1"
        },
        {
          "submenu": "zhihu-fisher.mediaDisplayMenu",
          "when": "view == zhihuHotList || view == zhihuRecommendList || view == zhihuSearchList || view == zhihuCollectionsList",
          "group": "bmode@2"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.configureBrowser",
          "when": "view == zhihuHotList || view == zhihuRecommendList || view == zhihuSearchList || view == zhihuCollectionsList",
          "group": "config@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.setCookie",
          "when": "view == zhihuHotList || view == zhihuRecommendList || view == zhihuSearchList || view == zhihuCollectionsList",
          "group": "config@2"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.clearCollectionCache",
          "when": "view == zhihuHotList || view == zhihuRecommendList || view == zhihuSearchList || view == zhihuCollectionsList",
          "group": "config@3"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.setAnswersPerBatch",
          "when": "view == zhihuHotList || view == zhihuRecommendList || view == zhihuSearchList || view == zhihuCollectionsList",
          "group": "config@4"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.toggleDebugMode",
          "when": "view == zhihuHotList || view == zhihuRecommendList || view == zhihuSearchList || view == zhihuCollectionsList",
          "group": "troubleshoot@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.restartExtension",
          "when": "view == zhihuHotList || view == zhihuRecommendList || view == zhihuSearchList || view == zhihuCollectionsList",
          "group": "troubleshoot@2"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.showTroubleshootingGuide",
          "when": "view == zhihuHotList || view == zhihuRecommendList || view == zhihuSearchList || view == zhihuCollectionsList",
          "group": "troubleshoot@3"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.openFeedback",
          "when": "view == zhihuHotList || view == zhihuRecommendList || view == zhihuSearchList || view == zhihuCollectionsList",
          "group": "ysupport@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.buyMeCoffee",
          "when": "view == zhihuHotList || view == zhihuRecommendList || view == zhihuSearchList || view == zhihuCollectionsList",
          "group": "ysupport@2"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.starOnGitHub",
          "when": "view == zhihuHotList || view == zhihuRecommendList || view == zhihuSearchList || view == zhihuCollectionsList",
          "group": "ysupport@3"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.showGuide",
          "when": "view == zhihuHotList || view == zhihuRecommendList || view == zhihuSearchList || view == zhihuCollectionsList",
          "group": "zhelp@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.showChangeLog",
          "when": "view == zhihuHotList || view == zhihuRecommendList || view == zhihuSearchList || view == zhihuCollectionsList",
          "group": "zhelp@2"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.showAbout",
          "when": "view == zhihuHotList || view == zhihuRecommendList || view == zhihuSearchList || view == zhihuCollectionsList",
          "group": "zhelp@3"
        }
      ],
      "zhihu-fisher.mediaDisplayMenu": [
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.setMediaModeNormal",
          "group": "1_media@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.setMediaModeMini",
          "group": "1_media@2"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.setMediaModeNone",
          "group": "1_media@3"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.setMiniMediaScale",
          "group": "2_scale@1"
        }
      ],
      "view/item/context": [
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.openInBrowser",
          "when": "view =~ /^zhihu(Hot|Recommend|Search)List$/ && (viewItem == TreeItem || viewItem == TreeItemWithImage)",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.showFullImage",
          "when": "view =~ /^zhihu(Hot|Recommend|Search)List$/ && viewItem == TreeItemWithImage",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.dislikeRecommendItem",
          "when": "view == zhihuRecommendList && (viewItem == TreeItem || viewItem == TreeItemWithImage)",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.favoriteRecommendItem",
          "when": "view == zhihuRecommendList && (viewItem == TreeItem || viewItem == TreeItemWithImage)",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.favoriteSearchItem",
          "when": "view == zhihuSearchList && (viewItem == TreeItem || viewItem == TreeItemWithImage)",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.dislikeAuthor",
          "when": "view == zhihuRecommendList && (viewItem == TreeItem || viewItem == TreeItemWithImage)",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.refreshCollection",
          "when": "view == zhihuCollectionsList && viewItem == collectionFolder",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.refreshCollection",
          "when": "view == zhihuCollectionsList && viewItem == myCollectionFolder",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.openCollectionInBrowser",
          "when": "view == zhihuCollectionsList && viewItem == collectionFolder",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.openCollectionInBrowser",
          "when": "view == zhihuCollectionsList && viewItem == myCollectionFolder",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.openCollectionItemInBrowser",
          "when": "view == zhihuCollectionsList && (viewItem == collectionItem || viewItem == collectionItemWithImage)",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.showCollectionItemImage",
          "when": "view == zhihuCollectionsList && viewItem == collectionItemWithImage",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.refreshMyCollections",
          "when": "view == zhihuCollectionsList && viewItem == myCollectionsRoot",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.createCollection",
          "when": "view == zhihuCollectionsList && viewItem == myCollectionsRoot",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.openMyCollectionsInBrowser",
          "when": "view == zhihuCollectionsList && viewItem == myCollectionsRoot",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.deleteCollection",
          "when": "view == zhihuCollectionsList && viewItem == myCollectionFolder",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.refreshFollowingCollections",
          "when": "view == zhihuCollectionsList && viewItem == followingCollectionsRoot",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.openFollowingCollectionsInBrowser",
          "when": "view == zhihuCollectionsList && viewItem == followingCollectionsRoot",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "zhihu-fisher.removeFromCollection",
          "when": "view == zhihuCollectionsList && viewItem =~ /.*removable.*/",
          "group": "inline"
        }
      ]
    },
    "walkthroughs": [
      {
        "id": "zhihu-fisher-getting-started",
        "title": "知乎摸鱼新手指南",
        "description": "了解如何使用知乎摸鱼插件的各项功能",
        "steps": [
          {
            "id": "welcome",
            "title": "欢迎使用知乎摸鱼！",
            "description": "**知乎摸鱼**是一个强大的VSCode扩展，让您可以直接在编辑器中浏览知乎内容。\n\n🌟 点击侧边栏的**📖**开始探索！",
            "media": {
              "markdown": "walkthrough/welcome.md"
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "setup-browser",
            "title": "第一步：配置浏览器",
            "description": "为了获得最佳体验，我们需要先配置浏览器引擎。插件会自动下载Chrome浏览器，但您也可以使用自己的浏览器。\n\n**自动配置（推荐）：**\n[配置浏览器](command:zhihu-fisher.configureBrowser)\n\n**手动配置：**\n[设置自定义浏览器路径](command:zhihu-fisher.setCustomChromePath)\n\n",
            "media": {
              "image": "https://img2024.cnblogs.com/blog/3085939/202504/3085939-20250425154308398-1262720236.png",
              "altText": "配置浏览器"
            },
            "completionEvents": [
              "onCommand:zhihu-fisher.configureBrowser",
              "onCommand:zhihu-fisher.setCustomChromePath"
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "setup-cookie",
            "title": "第二步：设置知乎Cookie",
            "description": "设置知乎Cookie可以访问更多内容，包括需要登录才能查看的文章和完整的评论。\n\n**快速设置：**\n1. 浏览器登录知乎，按F12打开开发者工具\n2. Network标签页找到知乎请求，复制Cookie值\n\n[设置知乎Cookie](command:zhihu-fisher.setCookie)\n\n**🔒 隐私说明：** Cookie仅本地存储，不会上传或分享。\n",
            "media": {
              "image": "https://img2024.cnblogs.com/blog/3085939/202504/3085939-20250424143443844-967882670.webp",
              "altText": "设置知乎Cookie"
            },
            "completionEvents": [
              "onCommand:zhihu-fisher.setCookie"
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "explore-content",
            "title": "第三步：开始探索内容",
            "description": "现在您可以开始浏览知乎内容了！\n\n[刷新热榜](command:zhihu-fisher.refreshHotList) | [刷新推荐](command:zhihu-fisher.refreshRecommendList) | [搜索内容](command:zhihu-fisher.searchContent)",
            "media": {
              "markdown": "walkthrough/explore-content.md"
            },
            "completionEvents": [
              "onCommand:zhihu-fisher.refreshHotList",
              "onCommand:zhihu-fisher.refreshRecommendList",
              "onCommand:zhihu-fisher.searchContent"
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "reading-features",
            "title": "第四步：文章阅读功能",
            "description": "在文章阅读界面体验丰富的功能：\n\n⌨️ **快捷键操作** - 高效的键盘导航和功能触发\n🎨 **5大设置面板** - 文本样式、多媒体、功能增强、工具栏、快捷键\n✨ **智能功能** - 灰色模式、智能伪装、自定义工具栏等",
            "media": {
              "markdown": "walkthrough/reading-features.md"
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "media-settings",
            "title": "第五步：自定义媒体显示",
            "description": "三种图片视频显示模式适应不同使用场景：\n\n[正常模式](command:zhihu-fisher.setMediaModeNormal) | [迷你模式](command:zhihu-fisher.setMediaModeMini) | [隐藏模式](command:zhihu-fisher.setMediaModeNone) | [设置缩放比例](command:zhihu-fisher.setMiniMediaScale)\n\n💡 **提示：** 在文章中按 `/` 键快速切换！",
            "media": {
              "markdown": "walkthrough/display-settings.md"
            },
            "completionEvents": [
